1
00:00:00,402 --> 00:00:08,594
Last week, my four-year-old daughter, Sally, was invited to a children's party.
上周,我4岁的女儿Sally被邀请去参加一个儿童聚会.

2
00:00:08,616 --> 00:00:12,424
I decided to take her by train.
我决定带她乘火车去.

3
00:00:12,425 --> 00:00:20,607
Sally was very excited because she had never travelled on a train before.
萨莉非常激动,因为她以前从未乘过火车.

4
00:00:20,608 --> 00:00:29,044
She sat near the window and asked questions about everything she saw.
她靠车窗坐着,对她所看到的一切都要问个明白.

5
00:00:29,045 --> 00:00:37,591
Suddenly, a middle-aged lady got on the train and sat opposite Sally.
突然,一个中年妇女上了火车,坐在Sally的对面.

6
00:00:37,592 --> 00:00:41,509
Hello, little girl,' she said.
“你好,小姑娘,”她说.

7
00:00:41,673 --> 00:00:47,348
Sally did not answer, but looked at her curiously.
Sally没回答,却好奇地看着她.

8
00:00:47,349 --> 00:00:54,439
The lady was dressed in a blue coat and a large, funny hat.
那位妇女穿着一件蓝色的大衣,戴着一顶大而滑稽的帽子.

9
00:00:54,440 --> 00:00:58,301
After the train had left the station, 
火车开出车站后,

10
00:00:58,302 --> 00:01:05,581
the lady opened her handbag and took out her powder compact.
那位妇女找开了手提包,拿出了她的粉盒.

11
00:01:05,582 --> 00:01:09,857
She then began to make up her face.
然后她开始打扮起来.

12
00:01:09,858 --> 00:01:14,024
Why are you doing that?' Sally asked.
“你为什么要那样做呢?”Sally问.

13
00:01:14,025 --> 00:01:18,750
To make myself beautiful,' the lady answered.
“为了把自己打扮漂亮啊,”那位妇女答道.

14
00:01:18,751 --> 00:01:23,879
She put away her compact and smiled kindly.
她收起来她的粉盒,慈祥地微笑着.

15
00:01:23,908 --> 00:01:28,346
But you are still ugly,' Sally said.
“可是你仍然很难看呀,”萨莉说.

16
00:01:28,347 --> 00:01:35,088
Sally was amused, but I was very embarrassed!
Sally感到很有趣,而我却很尴尬.

